{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vimeo/psalm/issues/2484","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vimeo/psalm","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vimeo/psalm/issues/2484/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vimeo/psalm/issues/2484/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vimeo/psalm/issues/2484/events","html_url":"https://github.com/vimeo/psalm/issues/2484","id":540160120,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU1NDAxNjAxMjA=","number":2484,"title":"Array type support with @psalm-assert-if-true","user":{"login":"ndench","id":2062388,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIwNjIzODg=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2062388?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/ndench","html_url":"https://github.com/ndench","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ndench/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ndench/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ndench/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ndench/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ndench/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ndench/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ndench/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ndench/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ndench/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":486061586,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWw0ODYwNjE1ODY=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vimeo/psalm/labels/bug","name":"bug","color":"ee0701","default":true,"description":null}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":2,"created_at":"2019-12-19T08:35:52Z","updated_at":"2019-12-19T19:24:32Z","closed_at":"2019-12-19T19:24:32Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"[Psalm assertions](https://psalm.dev/docs/annotating_code/adding_assertions/) don't seem to support [array types](https://psalm.dev/docs/annotating_code/type_syntax/array_types). It generates a `MissingDocBlockType` error, which I assume is because it reads the docblock as invalid because if I change `@psalm-assert-if-true array{type: string} $data` to `@psalm-assert-if-true array $data` the `MissingDocBlockType` error goes away.\r\n\r\nhttps://psalm.dev/r/754114d12f\r\n\r\n```php\r\n/**\r\n * @param mixed $data\r\n * @return bool\r\n * @psalm-assert-if-true array{type: string} $data\r\n */\r\nfunction isBar($data)\r\n{\r\n  return isset($data['type']);\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * @param mixed $data\r\n * @return string\r\n */\r\nfunction doBar($data)\r\n{\r\n  if (isBar($data)) {\r\n    return $data['type'];\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  throw new \\Exception();\r\n}\r\n```","closed_by":{"login":"muglug","id":2292638,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIyOTI2Mzg=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2292638?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug","html_url":"https://github.com/muglug","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vimeo/psalm/issues/2484/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh